    "Title": "Red Wind Straightforward Cargo Recovery",
    "Description": "RED WIND LINEHAUL\n'YOUR GOODS IN GOOD HANDS'\n----------------------------\n\nA Red Wind hauler has been ambushed by some outlaws and now our clients\u2019 cargo is sitting still whilst they prepare to steal it. We need a pilot with a <EM4>heavy-duty tractor beam</EM4> and a combat ready ship to head to the location below and recover the cargo before it\u2019s gone for good.\n\nRECOVERY LOCATION\n     \u00b7 <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>\n\nDROP OFF LOCATION\n     \u00b7 Freight elevator at <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4>\n\nThe pilot reported multiple hostiles so make sure you take this seriously. \n\nEVERY OPPORTUNITY COUNTS \u2013 Make the most of what\u2019s given to you, show us that you can handle more work.",
